- [x] `ServerScreenRenderer` receives `presentation.screen` and `presentation.intents`.

- [x] `ServerScreenRenderer` knows renderer kinds, not workflow step ids.

- [x] `ServerOperationRunner` receives `presentation.auto.nextOperation`.

- [x] `ServerOperationRunner` knows dispatch protocol kinds, not workflow meaning.

- [x] `LocalTransportOverlay` only shows local request/terminal transport failures.

- [x] Remove any mixed code where rendering logic starts operations.

