- [x] Keep code readable:
  - descriptive names
  - no nested watcher tricks
  - no hidden mutation from computed values
  - no magic timeouts for correctness
  - no deep branching by server internals

- [x] Add client unit tests around each concern.

- [x] Add Playwright tests confirming all major screens render through server fixtures.

